{
  "info": {
    "name": "Swap Jupiter - Solana 单网络全类型",
    "description": "Jupiter 渠道（Solana）API 测试用例：\n- 01-Jupiter-询价：同链主币<>代币、代币<>主币、代币<>代币（单网络，不使用多网络循环）\n- 02-Jupiter-构建：同链主币<>代币、代币<>主币、代币<>代币（严格校验 data.tx 存在）\n\n基线（来自 docs/qa/rules/swap-network-features.md）：\n- 网络 networkId: sol--101\n- userAddress / receivingAddress: 5UCR1u65cKhcJCnuaRxXy9zFYXnRBZ9ArYmGah6sEB52\n- SOL 主币标识: 空字符串\n- USDC: EPjFWdd5AufqSSqeM2qN1xzybapC8G4wEGGkZwyTDt1v\n- USDT: Es9vMFrzaCERmJfrF4H2FYD4KCoNkY11McCe8BenwNYB\n\nJupiter 渠道特性（来自 docs/qa/rules/swap-rules.md）：\n- Jupiter 按静态参数构建，不依赖 quoteResultCtx\n- /swap/v1/build-tx 必须返回 data.tx（Solana 序列化交易）",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "requestId",
      "value": "{{$guid}}",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "https://swap.onekeytest.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userAddressSolana",
      "value": "5UCR1u65cKhcJCnuaRxXy9zFYXnRBZ9ArYmGah6sEB52",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01-Jupiter-询价",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Quote - Jupiter - 主币<>代币 (SOL → USDC)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.variables.set('requestId', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Jupiter 主币<>代币 - HTTP 200', function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Jupiter 主币<>代币 - 业务码 0', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(0);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Jupiter 主币<>代币 - 返回包含 Jupiter 有效报价', function () {",
                  "  var data = json.data || [];",
                  "  var jupiterItem = data.find(function (x) {",
                  "    var p = x && x.info && x.info.provider;",
                  "    return p && String(p).toLowerCase().indexOf('jupiter') >= 0;",
                  "  });",
                  "  pm.expect(jupiterItem, 'data 中不存在 Jupiter 条目').to.not.be.undefined;",
                  "  pm.expect(jupiterItem.errorMessage, 'Jupiter 条目携带 errorMessage: ' + jupiterItem.errorMessage).to.be.oneOf([undefined, null, '']);",
                  "  var hasQuote = jupiterItem.toAmount || jupiterItem.fromAmount || (jupiterItem.info && jupiterItem.info.toAmount);",
                  "  pm.expect(hasQuote, 'Jupiter 条目无有效报价金额').to.be.ok;",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
